Expense Tracker

CodSoft Frontend Development Internship – Task 3

This project was developed as Task 3 of my CodSoft Frontend Development Internship. It is a responsive Expense Tracker application that helps users record and manage their income and expenses efficiently. The application is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript with a clean, modern, and user-friendly interface.

✨ Features

- Add income and expense transactions
- Track total balance, income, and expenses
- View transaction history
- Delete transactions
- Responsive design for all devices
- Clean and intuitive user interface
- Easy-to-use expense management

🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
